short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analyze your LinkedIn profile so that your University Career center can provide you feedback on improving it and grading it.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension to provide students career advisors, staff, and faculty at the university the ability to review a student's LinkedIn profile and comment on it to make it better. Only install it if your university has Quinncia. 

Quinncia Inc. or this app, is not affiliated with LinkedIn Corporation.
